      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i was just looking at some stuff about the heat death of the universe and i cant stop thinking about how everything we do is just... pointless. like every single thing we feel or build or try to achieve is just a temporary glitch in a system that's eventually just gonna be cold and empty forever. feels like we're just wasting energy for nothing.",
